            "type": "text",
            "text": "Kokoro Model Overview and Key Features"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Kokoro is designed for high-throughput, low-latency API workloads, supporting tasks like text generation, classification, and translation. Its architecture emphasizes scalability and ease of integration, with RESTful endpoints and support for batch processing. Key features include dynamic batching, automatic scaling, and comprehensive error handling, making it suitable for enterprise-grade applications."
          }
        ]
